Description: 10 Rugged Tablet- The Honeywell RT10A with the Android OS is a rugged tablet designed to keep workers and managers connected. The RT10A is easy to use with a 10.1-inch bright- high-resolution- optically bonded display. The FlexRange dual-lens imager is capable of scanning barcodes that are less than 0.1 m (5 in) or all the way out to 10.7 m (35 ft)- so users can easily capture barcodes from across the room without having to waste time getting close enough for a scan.
